 the delay finding images when page loaded or navigated ![new](https://img.shields.io/badge/-new-brightgreen)\n\n- option `locale` to support i18n config ![new](https://img.shields.io/badge/-new-brightgreen)\n\n---\n\n## 安装\n\n```bash\nnpm i -D vuepress-plugin-photo-swipe\n```\n\n或\n\n```bash\nyarn add -D vuepress-plugin-photo-swipe\n```\n\n## 从 V1 迁移\n\n- 选项 `delay`，控制页面加载和切换后寻找页面图片的延迟 ![新增](https://img.shields.io/badge/-新增-brightgreen)\n\n- 选项 `locale` 以支持国际化配置 ![新增](https://img.shields.io/badge/-新增-brightgreen)\n","readmeFilename":"README.md","_id":"vuepress-plugin-photo-swipe@2.0.0-alpha.32","_nodeVersion":"16.13.1","_npmVersion":"lerna/4.0.0/node@v16.13.1+x64 (win32)","dist":{"integrity":"sha512-/V59+8Oz9z+JzDFxLdJx8Lr+NQrWNjp1/JrROAMWKGRO0I7v/a5SfOt/1vvL11JL6K6Hf3bkaPhz58Rl7enSRA==","shasum":"7852ef9dfe6c0c5350ee0866215ece990b7c5fd0","tarball":"https://registry.npmjs.org/vuepress-plugin-photo-swipe/-/vuepress-plugin-photo-swipe-2.0.0-alpha.32.tgz","fileCount":20,"unpackedSize":53661,"npm-signature":"-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\r\nVersion: OpenPGP.js v4.10.10\r\nComment: https://openpgpjs.org\r\n\r\nwsFzBAEBCAAGBQJiEn0uACEJED1NWxICdlZqFiEECWMYAoorWMhJKdjhPU1b\r\nEgJ2Vmqz+w/+LVdkDYSekWUYBCrJHa9xjYI2t072wtqcXqK7cGyKYsXu/rvi\r\nlb9cokVJ0jKNGPxtnvfMnQqwrhG0NTaNjOB9uX6DK2B9HFWPBhC0kNyt0rXY\r\notvO7kLR7NTm/ZeYs0befrlJLZ7YZ2VQxCVx4MaegysCAKlymreRi7HqByUZ\r\noKRMSHsIkBDh33ZH2CcCOvnuw05SsGGuhtTuCnQlSMGJ1mr5Q0Nmio5qi1dQ\r\nEyvNExHlj31E0RsY1yuEtKarepkdofsxQKSLIs8eO+Wtn2GfpKtM7KtZ6E1f\r\n+qd1JW+Vl6PJ4SqPNGPGRBlgdRnyWmrQ/Lg/B3XmfFXfv4z1dujdCbX2YrXF\r\nHAmKk032A1XAFtlfAGkynRC9rBXqWYKxmBkaptlHIQvYmoRExgneTvziIcuv\r\nG4xFAl9kC+HOazXZEwdNvr3W275wRvPQEhtk7QcjfoOCBABMmsSGDw4j1MGO\r\nDK8yGHMvHY3thbpXUoA88UpRKqZCHLxTIM9VSmzrS+++UotMgV9R+Yss/TYj\r\nZ9Vln5b+MyU4tMZGFKej6KBzKJLfaqAavobfX/BxpTk2Hgmu8977er8DMhid\r\n97nV03QH9rlMoBjxaD32JM/k+1i/2gyL3SDS2DthRPJy1S6cj0zYwVwv5hno\r\nhJeTU6ZUOl8Jm4jHcn713wLlWCmzZye1x2A=\r\n=y5I4\r\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----\r\n","signatures":[{"keyid":"SH